  "detailed_description": "<h1>MEANDERS - OUR FIRST GAME!</h1><p><a href=\"http://store.steampowered.com/app/734920/MEANDERS/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  id=\"dynamiclink_0\" >http://store.steampowered.com/app/734920/MEANDERS/</a></a></p><br><h1>OVERCHUNKED - A TINY ADDICTIVE GAME</h1><p><a href=\"http://store.steampowered.com/app/833910/Overchunked/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  id=\"dynamiclink_1\" >http://store.steampowered.com/app/833910/Overchunked/</a></a></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/800300/extras/Glight_Gameplay60fps.png?t=1523593247\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>WELCOME TO THE ABYSS OF GLIGHT</strong></h2><br>Journey to the deepest end of the world.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Use the powers of both light and darkness to progress into a descending maze of puzzle and platform.<br><br></li><li> Be wary! Diving into the surrounding obscurity will strengthen your powers, but it will make coming back up far more difficult.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>ATOMIC STUFF</strong></h2>As our previous game, <a href=\"http://store.steampowered.com/app/734920/MEANDERS/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >MEANDERS</a></a>, Glight too will have crazy game and visual modes!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>However vast the darkness...</strong></h2><br><strong>What you currently see on GLIGHT Steam page is a prototype, and doesn't represent the final game style or art.</strong><br>Glight was submitted as an entry for the &quot;Epic Mega Jam 2017&quot;.<br>We will develop Glight into a full game and release it during 2018!<br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/800300/extras/EpicMegaJam_Glight.png?t=1523593247\" >",
  "about_the_game": "<img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/800300/extras/Glight_Gameplay60fps.png?t=1523593247\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>WELCOME TO THE ABYSS OF GLIGHT</strong></h2><br>Journey to the deepest end of the world.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Use the powers of both light and darkness to progress into a descending maze of puzzle and platform.<br><br></li><li> Be wary! Diving into the surrounding obscurity will strengthen your powers, but it will make coming back up far more difficult.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>ATOMIC STUFF</strong></h2>As our previous game, <a href=\"http://store.steampowered.com/app/734920/MEANDERS/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >MEANDERS</a></a>, Glight too will have crazy game and visual modes!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>However vast the darkness...</strong></h2><br><strong>What you currently see on GLIGHT Steam page is a prototype, and doesn't represent the final game style or art.</strong><br>Glight was submitted as an entry for the &quot;Epic Mega Jam 2017&quot;.<br>We will develop Glight into a full game and release it during 2018!<br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/800300/extras/EpicMegaJam_Glight.png?t=1523593247\" >",
